      <title>法院否决 Signa 债务计划，称其“显然不可行”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/court-nixes-signa-debt-plan-saying-it-s-obviously-not-feasible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利法院阻止了 Signa Prime Selection AG 的重组尝试，称由债权人支持的出售 Rene Benko 旗舰子公司所持有的财产的计划“显然不可行”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/court-nixes-signa-debt-plan-saying-it-s-obviously-not-feasible</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
